                    <span class="sc-about-chip">About Us</span>
                    <h1>Spaziocrypto - The Web3 <span>Community</span></h1>
                    <p>
                        Our vision is to become the leading italian reference point for information and
                        learning in the vast world of cryptocurrencies, blockchain technology and finance.
                        We are determined to create a virtuous environment where access to high quality
                        content is easy, understandable and useful to all.
                    </p>

